history.content:
Hi everyone!

 

Electrical Engineering and/or Computer Science can seem super broad--are you confused about what the different areas of EE/CS are or unsure what classes to take next? Have you taken the first lower divs? Then come out to the EE/CS Course Scheduling Workshop! HKN is partnering with CSM to host this workshop and it will be held on Monday, April 16th from 7 - 9 PM in Wozniak Lounge.

 

We will have upperclassmen who are familiar with a given area facilitate a discussion about that area (i.e. Computer Engineering, Machine Learning, or Circuits).

 

We hope to see you there!
